      "rationale": "Numerical solver error assessment beyond residual monitoring not required at MRL 2. Steady-state residuals converged to 1e-5 for all equations. Iterative convergence confirmed by monitoring NIH QoI stabilization. Factor not formally assessed per MRL 2 scoping decision."
    },
    {
