      "rationale": "Formal use error assessment not required at MRL 2. Analyst holds doctoral qualification in computational fluid dynamics with five years rotary blood pump simulation experience. Simulation setup reviewed by independent analyst. Use error risk considered low and within MRL 2 acceptance."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; model form selection justified by literature precedent.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published literature demonstrating suitability for centrifugal blood pump hemolysis prediction. Power law hemolysis model widely applied in regulatory submissions. Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2 and not performed."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
