      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; nominal inputs documented with traceability.",
      "rationale": "Nominal model inputs (fluid viscosity, density, pump geometry, rotational speed, flow boundary conditions) documented with traceability to measurement sources. Parametric sensitivity to input uncertainty not formally assessed at MRL 2. Input uncertainty considered manageable given well-characterized blood analog properties."
