      "rationale": "Qualitative comparison between validation model inputs and COU model inputs documented. Both use identical CFD setup, boundary condition types, and hemolysis model parameterization. Quantitative equivalency analysis not required at MRL 2. Equivalency considered sufficient for the intended credibility assessment."
